en_139604_1	The drugs were hidden inside a cargo of mineral ore being carried in lorries along a remote mountain pass leading to Chile's sea ports.
en_139604_2	Three men were arrested, a government official said.
en_139604_3	The haul has an estimated street value of $350m (£264m; €313m) in the US and came after a 10-month investigation.
en_139604_4	In January, Bolivian anti-drug police found eight tonnes of cocaine hidden within another consignment of mineral ore.
en_139604_5	Bolivia is the world's third largest producer of cocaine after Peru and Colombia.
